{"tid":1538484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"〈保持憤怒〉我地未贏呀","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:25:52.000Z","uid":156914,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"aa1deaa42a30278a012288b90845a666894479b8","tid":1538484,"uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:09:20.000Z","msg":"就算佢真係徹回都好，但我地未贏<br />\n<br />\n一日無普選、一日未還命、一日未清算鄉黑警<br />\n<br />\n我地都未贏呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/siVTzSC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsiVTzSC.jpg&h=5c510e56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n血債要血償"},{"pid":"c614e21b0cc8a72a52a8cdef423f32c8b01999da","tid":1538484,"uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:09:33.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"d0e008ff536e9059ea68d8196325eeeb94b2b4ac","tid":1538484,"uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:09:45.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"ec14e30be2789fa79af7ecde0d349dd015e0b38d","tid":1538484,"uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:09:59.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"91c0cdacd1a3b9e3e9e5873119d1b6618337149e","tid":1538484,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUGSMa3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUGSMa3.gif&h=1c74332a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【長期抗爭】最簡單有效嘅日常抗爭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538155</a>"},{"pid":"3b591a6e91bd1ad385ffda63823be6489440e712","tid":1538484,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:10:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d19ff790f1c1e5ba077ed3ced7fcd0151483f2","tid":1538484,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:10: